---
import ServiceLayout from '../../../../layouts/ServiceLayout.astro';
import RelatedServices from '../../../../components/RelatedServices.astro';
import CrossSiloLinks from '../../../../components/CrossSiloLinks.astro';

const pageData = {
  title: "Driving License Translation in Dubai – MOJ Certified | OnlineTranslation.ae",
  description: "Driving license translation in Dubai for RTA file opening and license conversion. MOJ-certified, approved countries list guidance, eye test and typing center process explained.",
  keywords: "driving license translation dubai, driving license translation UAE, MOJ certified license translation, RTA license conversion, foreign license translation dubai",
  heroTitle: "Driving License Translation in Dubai",
  heroSubtitle: "MOJ Certified for RTA File Opening",
  heroIntro: "Converting your foreign driving license to a UAE license requires a certified translation as the first step. Whether you are from an approved country eligible for direct conversion or need to go through the full testing process, the RTA requires your license to be translated by an MOJ-certified translator. We handle the translation quickly so you can proceed with your RTA appointment.",
  snapshot: [
    { icon: "clock", bold: "Digital drafts", text: "typically within 60 minutes" },
    { icon: "mobile-alt", bold: "WhatsApp-based workflow", text: "for easy communication" },
    { icon: "check-circle", bold: "Accepted by RTA", text: "for file opening" },
    { icon: "stamp", bold: "MOJ legal stamp", text: "with QR verification" }
  ],
  breadcrumbs: [
    { name: "Home", url: "/" },
    { name: "Personal Documents", url: "/personal/" },
    { name: "Immigration", url: "/personal/immigration/" },
    { name: "Driving License Translation", url: "/personal/immigration/license/" }
  ],
  
  trustStrip: [
    "MOJ-licensed partner",
    "Accepted by all RTA centers",
    "WhatsApp concierge support"
  ],
  
  processSteps: [
    {
      title: "Send your license photos",
      text: "Clear photos of front and back of your driving license. Include any endorsements or restrictions."
    },
    {
      title: "We prepare your translation",
      text: "MOJ-licensed translator creates RTA-ready translation with all license categories and validity dates."
    },
    {
      title: "Pickup or delivery",
      text: "Collect in Dubai or arrange courier. Many clients pick up on their way to the RTA center."
    }
  ],
  
  benefitCards: [
    {
      icon: "fast",
      title: "Same-day available",
      text: "Urgent RTA appointment? Express service gets your translation ready in hours, not days."
    },
    {
      icon: "document",
      title: "All categories included",
      text: "Motorcycle, car, truck, bus - all license categories translated and clearly formatted."
    },
    {
      icon: "shield",
      title: "Approved list guidance",
      text: "We can confirm if your country is on the RTA approved list for direct conversion."
    }
  ],
  
  accordionSections: [
    {
      title: "RTA license conversion process",
      id: "rta-process",
      items: [
        {
          heading: "Approved countries for direct conversion",
          body: "<p>The UAE maintains a list of countries whose driving licenses can be converted directly without a driving test. This list includes most Western European countries, the United States, Canada, Australia, New Zealand, Japan, South Korea, Singapore, South Africa, and all GCC countries.</p><p>If your country is on the approved list, you need only provide the translated license, pass an eye test, and complete the RTA application. We can confirm your country's status during document review.</p>"
        },
        {
          heading: "Countries requiring driving test",
          body: "<p>If your country is not on the approved list, you will need to take driving lessons at an RTA-approved driving school and pass the RTA driving test. The translated license is still required as part of your file opening.</p><p>Some nationalities have reduced lesson requirements based on their home country's driving standards.</p>"
        },
        {
          heading: "Eye test and typing center",
          body: "<p>After obtaining your translated license, you will need to visit a typing center to complete the RTA application forms and undergo an eye test. Many typing centers are located near RTA service centers.</p><p>The typing center will use your translated license to enter your details into the RTA system.</p>"
        },
        {
          heading: "License categories that can be converted",
          body: "<p>Standard car licenses (Category 2/B) are most commonly converted. Motorcycle licenses (Category 1/A) can also be converted from approved countries. Commercial categories such as heavy vehicles and buses have additional requirements.</p><p>Your translation will include all categories shown on your original license.</p>"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      title: "Special cases",
      id: "special-cases",
      items: [
        {
          heading: "Expired licenses",
          body: "<p>You can translate an expired license, but the RTA may have specific rules about how recently expired the license can be. Generally, licenses expired within the past few years are acceptable for conversion purposes.</p><p>Very old or long-expired licenses may require additional documentation from your home country.</p>"
        },
        {
          heading: "Digital or card-format licenses",
          body: "<p>Modern card-format licenses with information on both sides are common. We translate all information including the chip data representation, security features description, and any machine-readable zones if relevant to the RTA process.</p>"
        },
        {
          heading: "Licenses in non-Latin scripts",
          body: "<p>We translate licenses from any language including Arabic, Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Russian, Hindi, Urdu, and all European languages. Non-Latin script licenses are handled by translators familiar with those writing systems.</p>"
        },
        {
          heading: "International Driving Permit",
          body: "<p>An International Driving Permit (IDP) is not a substitute for license translation in the UAE conversion process. The RTA requires translation of your actual national driving license, not the IDP. However, an IDP may be useful for temporary driving before you complete the conversion.</p>"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  
  faqs: [
    {
      question: "Is my country on the RTA approved list for direct license conversion?",
      answer: "The approved list includes most Western European countries, USA, Canada, Australia, New Zealand, Japan, South Korea, Singapore, South Africa, and GCC countries. Send us a photo of your license and we can confirm your country's status and what process applies to you."
    },
    {
      question: "How long does driving license translation take?",
      answer: "Standard service delivers within 24 hours. Express service completes in 6 hours for urgent RTA appointments. Many clients order express service in the morning and collect before their afternoon RTA appointment."
    },
    {
      question: "What if my license is in Arabic already?",
      answer: "If your license is from a GCC country and already in Arabic, you may not need translation - the RTA can read it directly. However, some GCC licenses benefit from certified translation if any details are unclear or if additional documentation is needed."
    },
    {
      question: "Do you translate motorcycle licenses?",
      answer: "Yes. We translate all license categories including motorcycle (Category 1/A), light vehicle (Category 2/B), and commercial categories. All categories shown on your original license are included in the translation."
    },
    {
      question: "Can I use this translation at any RTA center?",
      answer: "Yes. Our MOJ-certified driving license translations are accepted at all RTA service centers across Dubai and the UAE. The translation includes the official stamp and QR verification that RTA staff can validate."
    }
  ],
  serviceType: "Driving License Translation"
};
---

<ServiceLayout {...pageData}>
  
  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>What You Receive</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Every driving license translation includes:</p>
      
      <div class="deliverables-grid">
        <div class="deliverable-card">
          <div class="deliverable-icon"><i class="fas fa-file-pdf"></i></div>
          <h3>Digital PDF Copy</h3>
          <p>Sent via WhatsApp and email. Some typing centers accept digital copies for file preparation.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="deliverable-card">
          <div class="deliverable-icon"><i class="fas fa-stamp"></i></div>
          <h3>MOJ-Stamped Original</h3>
          <p>Physical copy required by RTA. Includes official stamp, QR code, and translator license number.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="deliverable-card">
          <div class="deliverable-icon"><i class="fas fa-id-card"></i></div>
          <h3>All Categories Included</h3>
          <p>Every license category, restriction, and endorsement on your original license is translated.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="deliverable-card">
          <div class="deliverable-icon"><i class="fas fa-truck"></i></div>
          <h3>Pickup or Delivery</h3>
          <p>Collect from Dubai or have it delivered. Many clients pick up on their way to RTA.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-light">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Service Levels and Pricing</h2>
      <p class="section-intro">Choose based on your RTA appointment timing:</p>
      
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>Standard</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">AED 100</div>
          <p class="pricing-time">24-hour delivery</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>MOJ-certified translation</li>
            <li>Digital PDF + physical copy</li>
            <li>Free Dubai delivery</li>
            <li>WhatsApp updates</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pricing-card pricing-card--featured">
          <h3>Express</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">AED 180</div>
          <p class="pricing-time">6-hour delivery</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Everything in Standard</li>
            <li>Priority queue</li>
            <li>Same-day physical delivery</li>
            <li>RTA appointment coordination</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="pricing-card">
          <h3>VIP Concierge</h3>
          <div class="pricing-price">AED 300</div>
          <p class="pricing-time">1-hour draft</p>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>Everything in Express</li>
            <li>Immediate agent assignment</li>
            <li>Direct phone line</li>
            <li>RTA process guidance</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section bg-white">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>License Translation Across the UAE</h2>
      <div class="content-prose">
        <p>Residents across <a href="/locations/dubai/">Dubai</a>, <a href="/locations/abu-dhabi/">Abu Dhabi</a>, and <a href="/locations/sharjah/">Sharjah</a> use our driving license translation for RTA conversion. New arrivals often need license translation alongside <a href="/personal/immigration/">visa documentation</a> and <a href="/personal/immigration/pcc/">police clearance certificates</a>.</p>

        <p>For <a href="/services/golden-visa/">Golden Visa</a> holders, license conversion is a common post-arrival need. We also translate <a href="/personal/academic/degree/">degree certificates</a> and <a href="/personal/immigration/bank/">bank statements</a> for complete <a href="/personal/immigration/">immigration packages</a>.</p>
      </div>

      <RelatedServices pageKey="drivingLicense" showFamily={true} showPrerequisites={true} showNextSteps={true} showCrossSilo={true} maxItems={8} />
      <CrossSiloLinks maxLinks={6} />
    </div>
  </section>

</ServiceLayout>

<style>
  .section-intro {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  
  .deliverables-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .deliverable-card {
    background: #f8f9fa;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .deliverable-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: var(--primary-color);
    color: #ffffff;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .deliverable-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  
  .deliverable-card p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  
  .pricing-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .pricing-card {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 1rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .pricing-card--featured {
    border-color: var(--accent-color);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(255, 22, 84, 0.15);
  }
  
  .pricing-card h3 {
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
  }
  
  .pricing-price {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--primary-color);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }
  
  .pricing-time {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .pricing-features {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    text-align: left;
  }
  
  .pricing-features li {
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
  }
  
  .pricing-features li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent-color);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
</style>
